title: Housewives, Bachelorettes, and haters with Celebrity Makeup Artists Danielle Estrada
description: In today's episode, we sit down with makeup artist to the stars Danielle Estrada! Danielle's journey has been meteoric and went from 0-60 in just 2 years! She's worked with rappers, Housewives, Bachelorettes, and more! But it hasn't always been smooth sailing and we're talking about pushing past the haters and those that try to distract you from your dreams. Hang with us to get the dirt on her favorite celebrity client, how they are in real life, and get her advice on navigating a crazy career and going after your goals! Follow along @daniellemakeup_ on Instagram!
